{"word":"διάζωμα","slug":"διάζωμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διάζωμα</b></el> <el>(διάζωμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>διαζώννῡμι</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a girdle, drawers</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>subligaculum</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>an isthmus</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}